{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/debut-theme-product-page-images-zoom-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":889,"date":"2021-06-11T00:44:14","date_gmt":"2021-06-11T00:44:14","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=889"},"modified":"2021-06-11T04:59:57","modified_gmt":"2021-06-11T04:59:57","slug":"debut-theme-product-page-images-zoom-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/debut-theme-product-page-images-zoom-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Debut theme: Add a lightbox zoom to product page images (mobile &#038; desktop)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The Debut theme ships with a zoom on-hover feature out of the box, that is available exclusively for desktop. On mobile, depending of one&#8217;s device, there is still the possibility to &#8220;pinch-to-zoom&#8221; and, subsequently, have a better view of the product, but it&#8217;s rather a limited poor alternative especially when in comparison to popular e-commerce websites.<br><br>Today I&#8217;ll be teaching you how to quickly install a &#8220;lightbox zoom&#8221; feature for all of your Debut theme product page images, you just need to click (or tap) on the image to activate it. <br><br>It works out of the box on any Debut theme (including Debut themes using <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/debut-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">EZFY&#8217;s Debut Swipe Slider</a>) and just takes a couple of minutes to install.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-code-files\">Downloading the code files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can download the code files <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/debut-theme-zoom-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">clicking here</a>. (<a href=\"https://debut-theme-slider.myshopify.com/products/zoom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>)<br><br>Complete details about it can be found <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/debut-theme-zoom-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-1-opening-the-code-editor\">Step 1: opening the code editor</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Inside the <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/debut-theme-second-image-on-hover\" target=\"_blank\">.zip you downloaded</a> you&#8217;ll find two files: <ol><li><strong>ezfy-zoom.txt</strong></li><li><strong>settings_schema.txt</strong></li></ol></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-2-creating-the-lightbox-zoom-file\">Step 2: Creating the lightbox zoom file</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open the <strong>ezfy-zoom.txt </strong>file and copy all the code in there.</li><li>Now go back to your Shopify code editor and below <strong>Snippets</strong> click on &#8220;<em>Add a new snippet</em>&#8220;. Name it exactly: <strong>ezfy-zoom</strong><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1401\" height=\"698\" class=\"wp-image-894\" style=\"width: 650px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1.png 1401w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-600x299.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-1200x598.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-768x383.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1401px) 100vw, 1401px\" /><br></li><li>Paste the code that you copied and click on <strong>save</strong>.<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1564\" height=\"438\" class=\"wp-image-896\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2.jpg 1564w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-600x168.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-1200x336.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-768x215.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-1536x430.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1564px) 100vw, 1564px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-3-adding-the-code-to-the-product-pages\">Step 3: Adding the code to the product pages</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Find the file named <strong>theme.liquid</strong>.</li><li>Inside this file, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for:<br><br><strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong></li><li>Paste the following code&nbsp;<strong>before&nbsp;</strong>the&nbsp;<strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong>&nbsp;tag you found and save:<br><br><code>{% include 'ezfy-zoom' %}</code></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"720\" height=\"698\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-898\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3.jpg 720w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3-600x582.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-4th-and-final-step-updating-the-settings_schema-txt-file\">4th and final step: updating the settings_schema.txt file </h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open the <strong>settings_schema.txt </strong>file and copy all the code in there.</li><li>In your Shopify code editor find the <strong>settings_schema.json</strong> file in your theme.</li><li>Scroll all the way down.</li><li>Paste the code<strong> before</strong> the last line, after the <strong>} </strong>sign, as indicated the image below.<br><br>So, for example, in this case, the code should be pasted on the line <strong>1638 </strong>(the quantity of lines may vary depending of your theme, so don&#8217;t worry if it shows a different number on yours).<br> <img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"718\" height=\"753\" class=\"wp-image-900\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/zoom1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/zoom1.jpg 718w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/zoom1-600x629.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 718px) 100vw, 718px\" /><br>Paste the code to the right of the <strong>}</strong> character that the arrow is pointing to.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"617\" height=\"745\" class=\"wp-image-902\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/zoom3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/zoom3.jpg 617w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/zoom3-600x724.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 617px) 100vw, 617px\" /><br></li><li>Save and you&#8217;re ready to go!</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-troubleshooting-common-issues\">Troubleshooting common issues</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Question</strong>: It shows me an error after I edit the <strong>settings_schema.json</strong> file. What do I do?</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1023\" height=\"755\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/error1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-522\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/error1.jpg 1023w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/error1-600x443.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/error1-768x567.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 1023px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Answer</strong>: You very likely pasted the code at the bottom of the file. Please make sure you paste the code at the penultimate (second last) line as indicated in the <strong>step 4</strong>.<br><br>Your file must end with this character: <strong>]</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re still facing any issues please reach out to us via <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> and we&#8217;ll be more than happy to help you out!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-customizing-the-lightbox-zoom\">Customizing the lightbox zoom</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol id=\"block-1a8c9e4e-840d-4ccb-bb7c-3cba0d3cfcb3\"><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;<strong>Customize</strong>.<br><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg\" alt=\"Accessing the customize page on Shopify admin\"></li><li>Scroll all the way down and navigate to <strong>Theme settings &gt; EZFY Product Image Zoom</strong><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"473\" height=\"863\" class=\"wp-image-904\" style=\"width: 350px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/cc1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li><li>Inside the <strong>EZFY Product Image Zoom</strong> menu you&#8217;ll find all available options for the Lightbox Zoom.</li></ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Add a beautiful, smooth and minimalist lightbox zoom to the Debut theme product pages. Fully responsive, works on mobile and desktop.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":912,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[157],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/debut_lightbox_zoom-1-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/debut_lightbox_zoom-1-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/debut_lightbox_zoom-1-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["debut theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/debut_lightbox_zoom-1.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/889"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=889"}],"version-history":[{"count":11,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/889/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1605,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/889/revisions/1605"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/912"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=889"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=889"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=889"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["330429198","3356652627"]}